00:08:16.000 --> 00:08:21.000
That's a good pre-conference thing to watch for a lightning talk.

00:08:21.000 --> 00:08:31.000
Go start attending more data science hangouts now so that you can, like, pre-game up to conf, like, meet more people.

00:08:31.000 --> 00:08:36.000
All good advice.

00:08:36.000 --> 00:08:39.000
